name: Global X Equal Weight Canadian REITs Index ETF
longDescription: The Fund generally achieve objective by seeking the performance of an equal-weighted index designed to provide exposure to the top 10 Canadian real estate investment trusts (REITs) currently, the Mirae Asset Equal Weight Canadian REITs Index. The fund seeks to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible and net of expenses.
